OL,3,CPatient scans sent across to China and
OL,4,CAustrailia due to NI staffing crisis
OL,6,FHospitals are having to send patient X-
OL,7,FRays and CT and MRI scans to place
OL,8,Flike Australia and the United Arab
OL,9,FEmerits for analysis due to a shortage
OL,10,Fof radiologists in Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FInformation obtained by UTV under
OL,13,FFreedom of Information reveals that
OL,14,Falmost #20 million has been spent over
OL,15,Fthe past three years outsourcing the
OL,16,Fcritical service.
