OL,3,CPatient scans sent across to China and
OL,4,CAustrailia due to NI staffing crisis
OL,6,FIt comes as the Royal College of
OL,7,FRadiologists warns that if no action
OL,8,Fis taken to recruit and retain the
OL,9,Fworkforce then by 2029 there could be
OL,10,Fa 40 percent shortfall in radiologists
OL,11,Fhere - the worst shortage in the UK.
OL,13,FData from the Health Trusts show how
OL,14,Fthey are becoming increasingly reliant
OL,15,Fon external tele-radiology companies
OL,16,Fto provide the reading of scans from
OL,17,F6pm to 9am.
