OL,3,CPatient scans sent across to China and
OL,4,CAustrailia due to NI staffing crisis
OL,6,FAmaka Offiah, from the Royal College
OL,7,Fof Radiologists Northern Ireland says:
OL,8,F"In Northern Ireland there's a 27%
OL,9,Fshortfall, and if absolutely nothing
OL,10,Fwas done about that, then from five
OL,11,Fyears from the time of the census,
OL,12,Fwhich means 2029, that would increase
OL,13,Fto 41%. That would be the worst of all
OL,14,Fthe UK nations, that shortfall."
OL,16,FOffiah continued: "Certainly the ones
OL,17,Fgoing outside the country, there will
OL,18,Fbe an issue in terms of maintaining
OL,19,Fquality or and auditing.
