OL,11,FHealth Trust had the largest bill of
OL,12,F#5.8m. The Trust said some of their
OL,13,Fscans were outsourced across the UK
OL,14,Fand internationally - but did not
OL,15,Fprovide a list of those international
OL,16,Fcountries.
