OL,6,FThe Northern Trust spent #5.6 million,
OL,7,Fwith scans sent for reading not just
OL,8,Fin the UK, but also internationally to
OL,9,Fcountries like Australia, the US,
OL,10,FBahrain, China, Kuwait, Saudi Arabia
OL,11,Fand the United Arab Emirates
OL,13,F#5.1 million was spent by the Belfast
OL,14,FTrust, with their outsourced scans
OL,15,Fread by radiologists based in the UK.
OL,17,FAnd the Western Trust said #1.5
OL,18,Fmillion was spent over a three year
OL,19,Fperiod outsourcing to England.
