OL,6,FUnlike the other trusts the South
OL,7,FEastern Trust said no money was spent
OL,8,Fon assessing scans outside Northern
OL,9,FIreland.
OL,11,FMember of the NI Health Committee
OL,12,FDiane Dodds said: "Really what we want
OL,13,Fto do is invest in our local NHS. Make
OL,14,Fsure that we can report on scans from
OL,15,Fhere and make sure that we're giving
OL,16,Fpeople the best service that we can
OL,17,Fpossibly give.
